<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Core Metabolism — Interactive Study Series</title>
<meta name="description" content="A free, open-access interactive study series covering glycolysis, the Krebs cycle, oxidative phosphorylation, and metabolic integration. Three reading levels per topic. Built for students from high school through medical school.">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cinzel:wght@400;600;700;900&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
/* ===== TOKENS ===== */
:root {
  --bg:       #0d0e0f;
  --bg2:      #131516;
  --bg3:      #1a1c1e;
  --card:     #161819;
  --border:   #252829;
  --border2:  #2e3235;
  --text:     #eceae4;
  --text2:    #9a9590;
  --text3:    #5a5650;
  --mono:     'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
  --display:  'Cinzel', Georgia, serif;
  --sans:     'DM Sans', sans-serif;

  /* Module accent colors */
  --m1:       #4ecb71;   /* glycolysis — green */
  --m1b:      #2ea84e;
  --m1dim:    rgba(78,203,113,0.08);
  --m2:       #e8a030;   /* krebs — amber */
  --m2b:      #c8841a;
  --m2dim:    rgba(232,160,48,0.08);
  --m3:       #60a8e8;   /* oxphos — sky */
  --m3b:      #3a88c8;
  --m3dim:    rgba(96,168,232,0.08);
  --m4:       #50c8b0;   /* integration — teal */
  --m4b:      #2ea890;
  --m4dim:    rgba(80,200,176,0.08);

  --radius:   12px;
  --radius2:  20px;
}

*, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
  *, *::before, *::after {
    animation-duration: 0.01ms !important;
    transition-duration: 0.01ms !important;
  }
}

body {
  font-family: var(--sans);
  background: var(--bg);
  color: var(--text);
  min-height: 100vh;
  line-height: 1.7;
  overflow-x: hidden;
}

/* ===== SKIP LINK ===== */
.skip-link {
  position: absolute;
  top: -100%;
  left: 0;
  background: var(--m1);
  color: #050e08;
  padding: 10px 20px;
  font-weight: 600;
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  z-index: 9999;
  text-decoration: none;
  border-radius: 0 0 8px 0;
}
.skip-link:focus { top: 0; }

/* ===== BACKGROUND MESH ===== */
.bg-mesh {
  position: fixed;
  inset: 0;
  pointer-events: none;
  z-index: 0;
  background:
    radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 40% at 8% 12%,  rgba(78,203,113,0.04)  0%, transparent 55%),
    radial-gradient(ellipse 50% 60% at 92% 20%,  rgba(232,160,48,0.04)  0%, transparent 55%),
    radial-gradient(ellipse 55% 45% at 15% 88%,  rgba(96,168,232,0.03)  0%, transparent 55%),
    radial-gradient(ellipse 45% 55% at 88% 85%,  rgba(80,200,176,0.03)  0%, transparent 55%);
}

/* ===== NOISE TEXTURE OVERLAY ===== */
.bg-mesh::after {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  opacity: 0.018;
  background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 256 256' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='n'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.9' numOctaves='4' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23n)'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
  background-size: 180px 180px;
}

/* ===== LAYOUT ===== */
.page {
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
  max-width: 1080px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 0 28px 100px;
}

/* ===== HEADER ===== */
header {
  padding: 72px 0 56px;
  text-align: center;
  position: relative;
}
.series-tag {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 8px;
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: 0.68rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.18em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--text3);
  border: 1px solid var(--border2);
  padding: 5px 16px;
  border-radius: 50px;
  margin-bottom: 28px;
  animation: fadeUp 0.6s ease both;
}
.series-tag::before {
  content: '';
  display: inline-block;
  width: 6px;
  height: 6px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: var(--m1);
  animation: pulse 2.4s ease-in-out infinite;
}
@keyframes pulse {
  0%, 100% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }
  50% { opacity: 0.4; transform: scale(0.7); }
}
@keyframes fadeUp {
  from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(16px); }
  to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
}

h1 {
  font-family: var(--display);
  font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 6vw, 4.2rem);
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  line-height: 1.1;
  color: var(--text);
  margin-bottom: 10px;
  animation: fadeUp 0.6s 0.1s ease both;
}
h1 span {
  display: block;
  font-size: 0.42em;
  font-weight: 400;
  letter-spacing: 0.2em;
  color: var(--text3);
  text-transform: uppercase;
  margin-bottom: 10px;
}
.header-sub {
  font-size: 1.05rem;
  color: var(--text2);
  max-width: 580px;
  margin: 20px auto 0;
  line-height: 1.75;
  animation: fadeUp 0.6s 0.2s ease both;
}

/* ===== LEVEL LEGEND ===== */
.level-legend {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  gap: 20px;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  margin: 36px 0 0;
  animation: fadeUp 0.6s 0.3s ease both;
}
.legend-item {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 8px;
  font-size: 0.82rem;
  color: var(--text2);
}
.legend-dot {
  width: 8px;
  height: 8px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}

/* ===== PATHWAY CONNECTOR ===== */
.pathway-strip {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  gap: 0;
  margin: 52px 0 48px;
  animation: fadeUp 0.6s 0.35s ease both;
  overflow-x: auto;
  padding: 4px 0;
}
.pathway-node {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 6px;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}
.pathway-circle {
  width: 52px;
  height: 52px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  border: 2px solid;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: 0.72rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  position: relative;
  transition: transform 0.2s;
}
.pathway-circle:hover { transform: scale(1.1); }
.pathway-label {
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: 0.6rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--text3);
  text-align: center;
  max-width: 64px;
}
.pathway-arrow {
  flex: 1;
  min-width: 24px;
  max-width: 60px;
  height: 2px;
  position: relative;
  margin-bottom: 22px;
}
.pathway-arrow::after {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  right: -4px;
  top: -4px;
  border: 5px solid transparent;
  border-left-width: 8px;
}
.arr-m1 { background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--m1b), var(--m2b)); }
.arr-m1::after { border-left-color: var(--m2b); }
.arr-m2 { background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--m2b), var(--m3b)); }
.arr-m2::after { border-left-color: var(--m3b); }
.arr-m3 { background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--m3b), var(--m4b)); }
.arr-m3::after { border-left-color: var(--m4b); }
.pc-m1 { border-color: var(--m1); color: var(--m1); }
.pc-m2 { border-color: var(--m2); color: var(--m2); }
.pc-m3 { border-color: var(--m3); color: var(--m3); }
.pc-m4 { border-color: var(--m4); color: var(--m4); }

/* ===== MODULE GRID ===== */
.modules {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(460px, 1fr));
  gap: 24px;
  margin-bottom: 60px;
}
@media (max-width: 520px) {
  .modules { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
}

/* ===== MODULE CARD ===== */
.module-card {
  background: var(--card);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: var(--radius2);
  padding: 36px 38px;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
  transition: border-color 0.25s, transform 0.25s, box-shadow 0.25s;
  text-decoration: none;
  display: block;
}
.module-card::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
  height: 3px;
}
.module-card::after {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  opacity: 0;
  transition: opacity 0.25s;
  pointer-events: none;
}
.module-card:hover {
  transform: translateY(-3px);
  box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
}
.module-card:hover::after { opacity: 1; }
.module-card:focus-visible {
  outline: 2px solid var(--text2);
  outline-offset: 4px;
}

/* Per-module theming */
.card-m1::before { background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--m1), transparent); }
.card-m1::after  { background: var(--m1dim); }
.card-m1:hover   { border-color: var(--m1b); }
.card-m2::before { background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--m2), transparent); }
.card-m2::after  { background: var(--m2dim); }
.card-m2:hover   { border-color: var(--m2b); }
.card-m3::before { background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--m3), transparent); }
.card-m3::after  { background: var(--m3dim); }
.card-m3:hover   { border-color: var(--m3b); }
.card-m4::before { background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--m4), transparent); }
.card-m4::after  { background: var(--m4dim); }
.card-m4:hover   { border-color: var(--m4b); }

.card-inner { position: relative; z-index: 1; }

.module-num {
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: 0.65rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.14em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  margin-bottom: 14px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 10px;
}
.module-status {
  font-size: 0.62rem;
  padding: 3px 9px;
  border-radius: 50px;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.06em;
}
.status-live     { background: rgba(78,203,113,0.15); color: var(--m1); border: 1px solid rgba(78,203,113,0.25); }
.status-live-amb { background: rgba(232,160,48,0.12); color: var(--m2); border: 1px solid rgba(232,160,48,0.22); }
.status-soon     { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06); color: var(--text3); border: 1px solid var(--border2); }

.module-title {
  font-family: var(--display);
  font-size: 1.55rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  line-height: 1.25;
  color: var(--text);
  margin-bottom: 6px;
}
.module-subtitle {
  font-size: 0.82rem;
  color: var(--text3);
  font-family: var(--mono);
  letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
}
.module-desc {
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  color: var(--text2);
  line-height: 1.7;
  margin-bottom: 22px;
}

/* Topic pills */
.topic-pills {
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: 6px;
  margin-bottom: 26px;
}
.pill {
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: 0.62rem;
  padding: 4px 10px;
  border-radius: 50px;
  border: 1px solid var(--border2);
  color: var(--text3);
  letter-spacing: 0.04em;
}

/* Stats row */
.stats-row {
  display: flex;
  gap: 20px;
  margin-bottom: 24px;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}
.stat {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 2px;
}
.stat-val {
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  line-height: 1;
}
.stat-label {
  font-size: 0.68rem;
  color: var(--text3);
  letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
}

/* CTA */
.card-cta {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 9px;
  font-size: 0.88rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  padding: 10px 22px;
  border-radius: 8px;
  border: none;
  cursor: pointer;
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: all 0.18s;
}
.cta-m1 { background: var(--m1); color: #041008; }
.cta-m1:hover { background: #6cd885; }
.cta-m2 { background: var(--m2); color: #180e00; }
.cta-m2:hover { background: #f0b848; }
.cta-soon { background: var(--bg3); color: var(--text3); border: 1px solid var(--border2); cursor: default; }

.cta-arrow {
  display: inline-block;
  transition: transform 0.18s;
}
.module-card:hover .cta-arrow { transform: translateX(4px); }

/* Coming soon overlay */
.module-card.coming-soon {
  opacity: 0.65;
  pointer-events: none;
}
.module-card.coming-soon:hover {
  transform: none;
  box-shadow: none;
}

/* ===== WHAT'S INSIDE SECTION ===== */
.features-strip {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(200px, 1fr));
  gap: 1px;
  background: var(--border);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: var(--radius2);
  overflow: hidden;
  margin-bottom: 60px;
  animation: fadeUp 0.6s 0.45s ease both;
}
.feature-cell {
  background: var(--card);
  padding: 26px 24px;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 8px;
}
.feature-icon {
  font-size: 1.4rem;
  line-height: 1;
  margin-bottom: 2px;
}
.feature-title {
  font-family: var(--display);
  font-size: 0.92rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.03em;
  color: var(--text);
}
.feature-desc {
  font-size: 0.8rem;
  color: var(--text2);
  line-height: 1.6;
}

/* ===== LEVEL EXPLAINER ===== */
.level-explainer {
  background: var(--card);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: var(--radius2);
  padding: 36px 38px;
  margin-bottom: 60px;
  animation: fadeUp 0.6s 0.5s ease both;
}
.level-explainer h2 {
  font-family: var(--display);
  font-size: 1.3rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  color: var(--text);
  margin-bottom: 22px;
}
.level-rows {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 0;
}
.level-row {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 90px 1fr;
  gap: 20px;
  padding: 18px 0;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  align-items: start;
}
.level-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; padding-bottom: 0; }
.level-badge {
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: 0.72rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  padding: 5px 12px;
  border-radius: 50px;
  text-align: center;
  letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  white-space: nowrap;
}
.badge-l1 { background: rgba(78,203,113,0.12); color: var(--m1); border: 1px solid rgba(78,203,113,0.22); }
.badge-l2 { background: rgba(232,160,48,0.10); color: var(--m2); border: 1px solid rgba(232,160,48,0.2); }
.badge-l3 { background: rgba(96,168,232,0.10); color: var(--m3); border: 1px solid rgba(96,168,232,0.2); }
.level-row-text strong { color: var(--text); font-weight: 500; display: block; margin-bottom: 4px; font-size: 0.92rem; }
.level-row-text p { font-size: 0.84rem; color: var(--text2); line-height: 1.65; }

/* ===== FOOTER ===== */
footer {
  text-align: center;
  padding: 32px 0 0;
  border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
}
.footer-logo {
  font-family: var(--display);
  font-size: 1rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  color: var(--text3);
  margin-bottom: 10px;
}
.footer-note {
  font-size: 0.78rem;
  color: var(--text3);
  line-height: 1.7;
  max-width: 500px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}
.footer-note a { color: var(--text2); text-decoration: underline; text-underline-offset: 3px; }
.footer-note a:hover { color: var(--text); }
.footer-note a:focus-visible { outline: 2px solid var(--m1); outline-offset: 2px; }

/* ===== STAGGER ANIMATIONS ===== */
.module-card { animation: fadeUp 0.55s ease both; }
.card-m1 { animation-delay: 0.38s; }
.card-m2 { animation-delay: 0.46s; }
.card-m3 { animation-delay: 0.54s; }
.card-m4 { animation-delay: 0.62s; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<a class="skip-link" href="#main-content">Skip to main content</a>
<div class="bg-mesh" aria-hidden="true"></div>

<div class="page">

<header role="banner">
  <div class="series-tag" aria-label="Series status">Open Access · Free Forever</div>
  <h1>
    <span>Core Metabolism</span>
    An Interactive Study Series
  </h1>
  <p class="header-sub">From glucose to ATP — every pathway explained at three depths. Built for students who need to actually understand metabolism, not just memorize it.</p>

  <div class="level-legend" role="list" aria-label="Reading levels available in each module">
    <div class="legend-item" role="listitem">
      <div class="legend-dot" style="background:var(--m1)" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <span>Level 1 — Foundations</span>
    </div>
    <div class="legend-item" role="listitem">
      <div class="legend-dot" style="background:var(--m2)" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <span>Level 2 — Mechanisms</span>
    </div>
    <div class="legend-item" role="listitem">
      <div class="legend-dot" style="background:var(--m3)" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <span>Level 3 — Clinical &amp; Advanced</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<!-- PATHWAY DIAGRAM -->
<nav aria-label="Metabolic pathway overview">
  <div class="pathway-strip" role="list">
    <div class="pathway-node" role="listitem">
      <div class="pathway-circle pc-m1" aria-label="Module 1: Glycolysis">M1</div>
      <div class="pathway-label">Glycolysis</div>
    </div>
    <div class="pathway-arrow arr-m1" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="pathway-node" role="listitem">
      <div class="pathway-circle pc-m2" aria-label="Module 2: Krebs Cycle">M2</div>
      <div class="pathway-label">Krebs Cycle</div>
    </div>
    <div class="pathway-arrow arr-m2" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="pathway-node" role="listitem">
      <div class="pathway-circle pc-m3" aria-label="Module 3: Oxidative Phosphorylation">M3</div>
      <div class="pathway-label">Ox. Phos.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="pathway-arrow arr-m3" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="pathway-node" role="listitem">
      <div class="pathway-circle pc-m4" aria-label="Module 4: Integration">M4</div>
      <div class="pathway-label">Integration</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- MAIN CONTENT -->
<main id="main-content">

<!-- MODULE CARDS -->
<section aria-labelledby="modules-heading">
  <h2 id="modules-heading" class="sr-only">Study Modules</h2>
  <div class="modules">

    <!-- MODULE 1 -->
    <a class="module-card card-m1" href="glycolysis.html" aria-label="Module 1: Glycolysis and the Metabolism Gateway — available now">
      <div class="card-inner">
        <div class="module-num">
          <span style="color:var(--m1)">Module 01</span>
          <span class="module-status status-live" role="status">Live</span>
        </div>
        <div class="module-title">Glycolysis</div>
        <div class="module-subtitle">The Metabolism Gateway</div>
        <p class="module-desc">All ten steps, every enzyme, full regulation. Includes the pentose phosphate shunt, fate of pyruvate, and how glycolysis connects to every other pathway. Clinical connections throughout — from arsenic poisoning to the Warburg effect.</p>
        <div class="topic-pills" aria-label="Topics covered">
          <span class="pill">10 Steps</span>
          <span class="pill">PFK-1 Regulation</span>
          <span class="pill">Pentose Phosphate</span>
          <span class="pill">Pyruvate Fate</span>
          <span class="pill">Warburg Effect</span>
          <span class="pill">G6PD Deficiency</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stats-row" aria-label="Module statistics">
          <div class="stat">
            <span class="stat-val" style="color:var(--m1)">35</span>
            <span class="stat-label">MC Questions</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat">
            <span class="stat-val" style="color:var(--m1)">41</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Flashcards</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat">
            <span class="stat-val" style="color:var(--m1)">18</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Short Answers</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat">
            <span class="stat-val" style="color:var(--m1)">8</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Sections</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <span class="card-cta cta-m1" aria-hidden="true">
          Open Module <span class="cta-arrow">→</span>
        </span>
      </div>
    </a>

    <!-- MODULE 2 -->
    <a class="module-card card-m2" href="krebs-cycle.html" aria-label="Module 2: The Krebs Cycle — available now">
      <div class="card-inner">
        <div class="module-num">
          <span style="color:var(--m2)">Module 02</span>
          <span class="module-status status-live-amb" role="status">Live</span>
        </div>
